Class Admin

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.GREENWORKS.eco.data.Admin
  • @Entity
public class Admin
extends java.lang.Object
    The Admin class is for handling admin related database transactions. This class is exclusively used for verifying user credentials in the admin panel.
